1.Write a module that takes 2 inputs a, b and outputs their AND gate One line using assign.

module and_gate(
    input a,
    input b,
    output y
);
  assign y = a||b;
endmodule

2.Write a module that takes 1 input a and outputs its NOT gate One line using assign.

 module not_gate(
   input a,
   output y
 );

 assign y = ~a;
endmodule

